  "A pharmacist uses the linear approximation of f(x) = e^x at x = 0 to estimate the dosage adjustment e^(0.05). What is the estimated value?": "药剂师使用f(x) = exxx = 0的直线近似值估计剂量调整e(0.05)。 估计值是多少?",
