  "A weather scientist models temperature as T(x) = 70 + 5sin(x) degrees. Using a tangent line approximation at x = 0, estimate the temperature at x = 0.2 radians.": "气象科学家模拟温度为 T(x) = 70 + 5sin(x) 度。使用x = 0 的正切线近似值,估计 x = 0 = 0. 2 弧度的温度。",
